That's true,

00:07:17.890 --> 00:07:19.130
I really should congratulate you.

00:07:19.450 --> 00:07:21.240
But it seems like

00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:22.280
you're not too happy about it.

00:07:24.040 --> 00:07:25.210
It cost me a life,

00:07:26.040 --> 00:07:27.760
for the position of a carriage steward.

00:07:28.450 --> 00:07:29.280
After all,

00:07:29.890 --> 00:07:31.130
it's just a job managing horses.

00:07:33.130 --> 00:07:35.730
What does it matter, steward or horse manager?

00:07:35.890 --> 00:07:36.800
In Xichuan,

00:07:37.690 --> 00:07:38.280
no,

00:07:39.690 --> 00:07:40.860
in this world,

00:07:40.890 --> 00:07:42.730
you never know when your time will come.

00:07:43.250 --> 00:07:44.260
