00:12:59.890 --> 00:13:00.970
If it wasn't him,

00:13:00.970 --> 00:13:01.850
then who could it be?

00:13:06.970 --> 00:13:08.520
Is there any other evidences?

00:13:08.970 --> 00:13:09.850
Present the physical evidence.

00:13:17.120 --> 00:13:19.160
This is the murder weapon found at the scene.

00:13:26.600 --> 00:13:27.410
What does this mean?

00:13:27.520 --> 00:13:28.370
Take it.

00:13:30.080 --> 00:13:32.370
I believe trouble clings to you.

00:13:32.720 --> 00:13:33.970
We just arrived in Xichuan,

00:13:33.970 --> 00:13:35.250
haven't even entered the gate,

00:13:35.390 --> 00:13:36.530
and you've caused a such trouble.

00:13:37.520 --> 00:13:39.160
If Wen Jue hadn't arrived in time,

00:13:39.290 --> 00:13:41.000
we would have died here.

00:13:42.720 --> 00:13:43.970
The Three Heroes of Xichuan.

00:13:48.040 --> 00:13:48.970
Tell everyone,

00:13:49.330 --> 00:13:50.370
where have you seen this?

00:13:55.560 --> 00:13:56.370
Speak!

00:14:00.040 --> 00:14:01.290
The Fortune Inn.

00:14:01.600 --> 00:14:03.200
Both the witnesses and physical evidence are present.

00:14:03.290 --> 00:14:05.370
Is Mr. Wen satisfied now?

00:14:06.770 --> 00:14:07.330
Nonsense!

00:14:07.770 --> 00:14:09.000
This dagger is mine.

00:14:12.560 --> 00:14:14.720
It was a gift from Fu Sheng.

00:14:15.370 --> 00:14:16.000
Father,

00:14:16.970 --> 00:14:17.930
you must tell them.

00:14:22.000 --> 00:14:22.810
Indeed,

00:14:23.640 --> 00:14:24.600
this dagger

00:14:25.160 --> 00:14:27.720
was indeed gifted to my daughter by Physician Fu.

00:14:28.490 --> 00:14:31.450
However, as I've always disliked her handling weapons,

00:14:32.080 --> 00:14:33.770
I took it away and discarded it.

00:14:34.160 --> 00:14:37.040
Never did I imagine it would appear at the scene of the crime.

00:14:37.160 --> 00:14:38.000
Vice Chairman Li,

00:14:38.370 --> 00:14:39.160
this time

00:14:39.160 --> 00:14:41.120
you've really arrested the wrong person.

00:14:42.520 --> 00:14:44.030
It seems Lord Wen

00:14:44.030 --> 00:14:46.250
is determined to protect the murderers.

00:14:46.560 --> 00:14:49.250
Since neither the witnesses nor material evidence counts,

00:14:50.120 --> 00:14:50.890
then

00:14:51.490 --> 00:14:53.160
it wouldn't be right to convict easily.

00:14:54.040 --> 00:14:54.970
How about this,

00:14:55.100 --> 00:14:56.000
from now on,

00:14:56.330 --> 00:14:57.770
my Lord's Mansion

00:14:57.770 --> 00:14:59.160
will issue a bounty notice

00:14:59.930 --> 00:15:03.000
together with Jibei Chamber of Commerce to capture the real murderer.

00:15:03.490 --> 00:15:05.450
And give Chairman Song justice.

00:15:06.370 --> 00:15:07.490
As for

00:15:07.710 --> 00:15:08.750
these two

00:15:09.850 --> 00:15:12.120
injured by Vice Chairman Li by mistake,

00:15:14.450 --> 00:15:15.970
I will make decisions on their behalf.

